- As shown above. More a deck design, but the key cards are @{"Kurlan Naiskos" link COTD13}
  and perhaps a @{"Bynars' Weapon Enhancement" link "STCCG:cotd200.guide/COTD197"} (WEAPONS 33 - Kill those pesky
  outposts!)

